  "layerReason": "This package primarily orchestrates the flow of data and state management for the Bitcoin wallet application, connecting various components and ensuring that updates are communicated effectively. It does not focus on user interface elements, which would be characteristic of the Presentation Layer, nor does it encapsulate core business logic or domain-specific computations typical of the Domain Layer. Additionally, while it interacts with data sources, its main role is to manage application flow rather than perform direct data access operations, which would be the focus of the Data Source Layer."
}

