  "layerReason": "The classes in this package are primarily focused on orchestrating the flow of Bitcoin payment transactions via Bluetooth and HTTP, which aligns with the responsibilities of the service layer. They act as service providers that handle the application logic related to payment processing. The package does not manage user interface elements, which would be characteristic of the presentation layer, nor does it encapsulate business logic or domain data, which would be typical of the domain layer. Additionally, it does not interact directly with data sources, which would be the focus of the data source layer."
