  "description": "This package is designed to manage blockchain operations, facilitate communication with the blockchain network, and handle various services related to the Bitcoin wallet application.",
  "layer": "Service Layer",
  "layerReason": "The classes in this package primarily provide services that orchestrate interactions between the application and the blockchain, manage notifications, and handle user interactions related to transactions and connectivity. They do not directly manage user interface elements, which would be characteristic of the Presentation Layer, nor do they encapsulate core business logic or domain data, which would be typical of the Domain Layer. Additionally, there is no interaction with data sources or persistence mechanisms that would define the Data Source Layer."
